      72.02,
      36.47,
      524.96,
      63.55
    ],
    "text": "Implementation of a Traffic Plan in Conjunction with a Special Service at St. Anthony\u2019s Church, Kochchikade",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      78.13,
      526.01,
      119.01
    ],
    "text": "In view of the 7th anniversary of the Easter Sunday attacks, a special traffic management plan will be implemented in connection with a commemorative religious service scheduled to be held at St. Anthony\u2019s Church on 21.04.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      133.45,
      481.04,
      160.53
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, vehicular movement will be restricted on roads surrounding the church premises from 7:00 a.m. on 21.04.2026 until the conclusion of the service.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      175.09,
      497.47,
      202.17
    ],
    "text": "Media institutions are kindly requested to disseminate this information to the public and motorists to ensure awareness and minimize inconvenience.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
